{"tid":626679,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"匈牙利大選　假黨林立　有政黨搵人雞叫　國營電視台訪談　獨佔五分鐘","createTime":"2018-04-12T10:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T10:11:23.000Z","uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f37111f9c551d2f1e1c0c080f93993dbaa8c2f48","tid":626679,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T10:11:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://gaus.ee/2018/04/cluck-cluck-kadesh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgaus.ee%2F2018%2F04%2Fcluck-cluck-kadesh%2F&d=jWlCGUlyUx1sda%2BvdaxSjB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=f4b18398\" target=\"_blank\">http://gaus.ee/2018/04/cluck-cluck-kadesh/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://gaus.ee/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Screenshot-2018-04-09-16.18.23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgaus.ee%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2FScreenshot-2018-04-09-16.18.23.png&h=54176238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n布達佩斯 &ndash; 匈牙利大選結果係早已預料，因此出現唔少惡搞政黨，甚至假政黨cap水。<br />\n<br />\n因為匈牙利民主化期間未鼓勵參選，若一個政黨能提名27位候選人，政府就會提供資助。今年大選至少14個假黨，花費高達950萬歐。<br />\n<br />\n但有啲假黨，或者惡搞黨比較認證，例如兩條狗尾黨 (MKKP)，係匈牙利文兩條狗尾，就好似「第三條腿」咁嘅性暗示。<br />\n<br />\n而佢地政綱包括用直升機取代校巴，以及同其他星球做貿易，而且佢地候選人往往唔係一般人，或者係造型獨特，經常有假扮其他動物。<br />\n<br />\n甚至佢地派出一位雞頭造型嘅候選人，出席國營電視台候選政黨每個黨都有嘅5分鐘答問時間，無論任何問題，都只有一個答案，就係雞叫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j-RC6IEp7iQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dj-RC6IEp7iQ&d=jWlCGUlyUx1sda%2BvdaxSjB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=506901a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j-RC6IEp7iQ</a>"}]}